        <updateDate>2019-08-30T11:32:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Congressional Vehicle Leases Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits funds provided for the operations of a chamber of Congress from being used to lease a vehicle for: (1) more than 30 consecutive days, or (2) any period of time at a daily rate exceeding a maximum rate established by regulation. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
